。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"05dbad2567"},{"id":"3548d5c25d","type":"subtitle","text":"“火山”报(川大经二  大字报)","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"05dbad2567"},{"id":"6359c1c378","type":"paragraph","text":"入党秘诀","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"05dbad2567"},{"id":"42c6b4bb01","type":"paragraph","text":"1．缺才不学，只要守本分    　2．群众可不管，只要善奉迎","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"05dbad2567"},{"id":"a3c1523746","type":"paragraph","text":"3．政治水平低，快把洋号吹    4．如想入党快，快找拉线人","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"05dbad2567"},{"id":"15fd29a150","type":"paragraph","text":"(历史系58级一群)","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"05dbad2567"}],"page":{"id":"52306c8785","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"05dbad2567","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}